1, Brew install GEMU
brew install GEMU

2. Download and install UTM
https://rockylinux.org/download
Download the ARM(aarch64) for Apple M4 CPU

3. Just download the free utm from this side 
Go to https://mac.getutm.app/

Save and move into application 

4. Start UTM and config the new VM

5. After start the vm, config the static IP. 

6. Clone VM. 

 
